| comment "Dragnet [Ransomware]: dragnet-ransomware-2024-1015 — Recovery Inhibition (lockbit3)"
| comment "Status: experimental | Level: high | ID: bc44ffd9-445f-5d9b-b477-4b69f67c9a9e"
